data.title: chan Vol. 8 (episodes 428 to 448)
data.meta_description: Vocab for episodes 428 to 448 of the animated series ‘Crayon Shin-chan’. This is volume 8/25. Vocab already listed in past volumes is not included. Check out the ‘Most Common Vocab’ set (vol 0) for a list of the most common terms throughout the series.
